{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeVertical","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"case","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"codeListing","code":[" If a text's language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out vertically."],"syntax":null}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeVertical":{"title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","role":"symbol","abstract":[],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","role":"symbol","title":"MLNTextWritingMode","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingMode"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"}}}